channel.title: My cliently randomly stopped loading properly
channel.description:
Everything was fine until yesterday. It just randomly doesn't load right. It takes at least 10 minutes to pull up the login screen, and it's laggy as anything when I log in. But it's only on this one computer for some reason... If I go to another computer and use, it's fine. The runbox doesn't say anything, but it's just really weird. Any ideas?
Thanks.
